title: Sibling Advicery: Fake Friends/Grindr Tips
description:
Bob and Monet ring in the new year with a new episode of Sibling Advicery! Bob begs those in their 20s to open Roth IRAs, Monét explains that she's done making new friends, and the two of them give advice on navigating Tinder and quitting church. Don't miss Bob's cover of Adele's Someone Like You!!
DON’T MISS THE SEASON PREMIERE OF RUPAUL’S DRAG RACE. FRIDAY, JANUARY 7TH AT 8/7 CENTRAL ONLY ON VH1.
